A '''flight group''' was a unit of [[starfighter]]s. The [[Galactic Empire]] used flight groups, such as [[Alpha Flight Group]] and [[Omega Flight Group]].<ref name="Battlefront">''[[Star Wars Battlefront]]''</ref> The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic|Rebel Alliance]] also utilized them, including [[Exeter Group]], [[Feral Group]] and [[Cobalt Group]].<ref name="Shattered Empire II">[[Shattered Empire 2|''Shattered Empire'' 2]]</ref> During the [[Battle of Theed]], three [[N-1 starfighter]]s flew as a flight group led by Rebel Alliance [[Lieutenant]] [[Shara Bey]].<ref name="SE 3" />

